4,' alt='Surface Pen' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/b9792cf6089fae2fa1df690a4f5b0531/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/b9792cf6089fae2fa1df690a4f5b0531/width(3000).jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Surface Pro Type Cover</h3>Surface Pro Type Cover is ultra-slim, yet performs like a full, traditional laptop keyboard.&nbsp;<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>Surface Pen</h3>Better and faster than ever, with tilt for shading, greater sensitivity, and virtually no lag to help you capture your thoughts and get more done.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='left'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/e02bf2ec033943495937415f742e882a/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Your laptop, your way' title='Your laptop, your way show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Your laptop, your way' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/e02bf2ec033943495937415f742e882a/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/e02bf2ec033943495937415f742e882a/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Your laptop, your way</h3>Work and play your way virtually anywhere. With laptop-to-tablet versatility, plus better connectivity with USB-C™ and USB-A ports, ultra-slim and light Surface Pro 7 adapts to you.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/82cb9f8e86ab0ebf897d360fdcb6ac8d/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas' title='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/82cb9f8e86ab0ebf897d360fdcb6ac8d/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/82cb9f8e86ab0ebf897d360fdcb6ac8d/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Next-gen power to fuel your ideas</h3>Wherever you go, and whatever you do, next-generation Surface Pro 7 stands ready. With its laptop-class Intel® Core™ processor, Fast Charging, all-day battery,<sup data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>1</sup> and Instant On, you can get back to work whenever inspiration strikes.&nbsp;<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='left'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/02da4921cb36c66ac00742e8750d7ed5/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Express yourself' title='Express yourself show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src=